@startuml ch5_fig_crispdm
!include _style.iuml
title CRISP-DM lifecycle mapped onto the canvas pipeline

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

() "Pipeline\n(canvas)" as core

rectangle "1. Business\nUnderstanding" as B
rectangle "2. Data\nUnderstanding" as D
rectangle "3. Data\nPreparation" as P
rectangle "4. Modelling" as M
rectangle "5. Evaluation" as E
rectangle "6. Deployment" as DEP

B -down-> D
D -down-> P
P -right-> M
M -up-> E
E -up-> B
E -right-> DEP

B .. core
D .. core
P .. core
M .. core
E .. core
DEP .. core

note right of B
  Identify the supervised tasks
  a non-technical user can describe.
  Surface 14 algorithms behind
  a single Train node.
end note
note right of D
  Reuse the profile produced by the
  ingestion service: missing, skew,
  imbalance, correlations.
end note
note right of P
  Celery task: 70/15/15 split,
  column-wise imputation, scaling,
  one-hot vs target encoding.
end note
note right of M
  BaseMLModel subclasses, one
  signature across sklearn / H2O /
  XGB / LightGBM / CatBoost / Prophet.
end note
note right of E
  Accuracy/F1/AUC or R²/MAE/RMSE.
  TreeSHAP for tree-based models.
end note
note right of DEP
  Model registry with versioning.
  Downloadable joblib + FastAPI zip.
end note
@enduml
